286
00:20:26.770 --> 00:20:27.940
Yeah?

287
00:20:28.690 --> 00:20:29.690
Every day.

288
00:20:32.070 --> 00:20:33.070
That's good.

289
00:20:38.820 --> 00:20:39.990
And the boy that…

290
00:20:41.030 --> 00:20:43.700
Do you… do you know where
they put him? Whitecross. was it?

291
00:20:45.410 --> 00:20:46.410
Redheath.

292
00:20:47.210 --> 00:20:48.210
Redheath.

293
00:20:50.080 --> 00:20:51.330
And is he…

294
00:20:52.590 --> 00:20:54.026
