300
00:21:11.150 --> 00:21:12.336
Nothing. Nothing.

301
00:21:12.360 --> 00:21:14.570
I was… I was just… I
was just checking in.

302
00:21:15.730 --> 00:21:17.980
'Cause you know what they
called it. the judge and that?

303
00:21:18.610 --> 00:21:21.296
"An act of cold-blooded. callous cruelty."

304
00:21:21.320 --> 00:21:23.966
- I know.
- "Callous cruelty."

305
00:21:23.990 --> 00:21:25.080
I know.

306
00:21:25.870 --> 00:21:27.750
She was my daughter.

307
00:21:28.460 --> 00:21:30.806
- She was my only child.
- I know.

308
00:21:30.830 --> 00:21:33.856
And as far as I'm concerned.
he can fucking well die in there.

309
00:21:33.880 --> 00:21:35.260
So. last chance. yeah.

310
00:21:35.840 --> 00:21:37.470
What is it you want to say?

311
00:21:41.260 --> 00:21:42.390
Nothing.

312
00:21:45.350 --> 00:21:46.350
Nothing.

313
00:21:47.640 --> 00:21:49.680
I'm so sorry. I didn't mean to scare you.

314
00:21:51.770 --> 00:21:52.810
Okay?

315
00:21:54.610 --> 00:21:55.860
It's okay.

316
00:21:57.730 --> 00:21:58.900
Come on. then.

317
00:21:59.530 --> 00:22:02.580
