- Come on. Ashley.

321
00:22:23.550 --> 00:22:25.760
This way. There you go. Just here.

322
00:22:30.180 --> 00:22:31.260
June.

323
00:22:32.770 --> 00:22:34.690
"I'm king of the world!"

324
00:22:36.150 --> 00:22:37.610
Come and see me.

325
00:23:31.330 --> 00:23:33.806
