349
00:24:31.310 --> 00:24:33.576
"Safeguarding"? Wow. Okay.

350
00:24:33.600 --> 00:24:34.600
That's a…

351
00:24:35.730 --> 00:24:36.810
That's a new one.

352
00:24:37.350 --> 00:24:38.350
Look…

353
00:24:40.020 --> 00:24:42.230
Could you just please
just tell me where he is?

354
00:24:42.730 --> 00:24:46.296
Here's what we can do. Why
don't you give me your number?

355
00:24:46.320 --> 00:24:48.660
And I'll call you as soon
