358
00:25:03.300 --> 00:25:04.300
Yeah.

359
00:25:05.260 --> 00:25:08.856
You sure? 'Cause we can
reschedule if you like. you know?

360
00:25:08.880 --> 00:25:10.816
Yeah. I want to get my money's worth.

361
00:25:10.840 --> 00:25:12.260
What's with the…

362
00:25:13.010 --> 00:25:14.720
