- What?

363
00:25:15.310 --> 00:25:16.456
Am I meant to be dressed up?

364
00:25:16.480 --> 00:25:17.730
What? Like date night?

365
00:25:18.310 --> 00:25:19.690
Yeah. date night for screw ups.

366
00:25:22.770 --> 00:25:24.570
Come on. It's your
favorite hour of the week.

367
00:25:39.370 --> 00:25:40.410
Hi.

368
00:25:42.130 --> 00:25:43.380
So…

369
00:25:44.460 --> 00:25:46.090
How have we been getting on?

370
00:25:48.170 --> 00:25:49.420
Who wants to start?

371
00:25:55.260 --> 00:25:56.680
That was good. wasn't it?

372
00:25:58.350 --> 00:25:59.350
Useful.

373
00:26:00.270 --> 00:26:02.520
Safety valve or… or whatever.

374
00:26:03.610 --> 00:26:04.610
Shut up.

375
00:26:05.940 --> 00:26:06.940
What?

376
00:26:07.650 --> 00:26:08.730
You fancy her.

377
00:26:10.700 --> 00:26:12.176
